Individuals will be expected to:
- Attend to clients, understand and note their requirements for corporate secretarial
services
- Explain and advise the clients accordingly in the area of corporate secretarial matters
- Incorporation of companies and registration of businesses
- Preparation of resolutions, minutes and statutory returns
- E-submission of notifications to ACRA
- Assist in scheduling, co-ordination of and attendance at shareholders/board meetings
- Ensure maintenance of statutory registers and minute books
- Other ad hoc corporate secretarial duties